## OpenFlights airlines.dat (Open Database License v1.0)

The file `src/Yaat.Sim/Speech/Data/airlines.tsv` is a Derivative Database
extracted from OpenFlights' `airlines.dat`.

  Upstream: https://openflights.org/data.html
  License:  Open Database License (ODbL) v1.0
  Full license text: src/Yaat.Sim/Speech/Data/LICENSE-OPENFLIGHTS.txt

Attribution: "Airline telephony data derived from OpenFlights
(https://openflights.org/data.html), licensed under ODbL 1.0."

YAAT's MIT license governs the source code; ODbL governs only the
`airlines.tsv` file. ODbL § 4.5a exempts compiled binaries (Produced
Works) from the share-alike requirement, so `Yaat.Sim.dll` and the
YAAT installer are distributed under YAAT's MIT terms.
